	4.2	Staff Gold Investment Account (GIA)	i)	Selling price for staff GIA purchase transaction:
		Average GIA price * + 0.555% of the average GIA price
		
	ii)	Buying price for staff GIA sale transaction:
		Average GIA price * - 0.555% of the average GIA price.
	* Average GIA price =
	   The Bank's Selling Price (BSP) +
	   Bank's Buying Price (BBP)
	     _____________________________________________________________
	
	                            2
	
	where BSP and BBP are the prevailing gold prices at the point of transaction.
